l} drawn</string><string name="counterCategorySummary">{cat}: {n} remaining</string><string name="counterCatRemainHeading">{cat} — {n} remaining</string><string name="counterSrNoCategoryTiles">This army has no {cat} tiles in the deck.</string><string name="counterNoTilesDrawn">No tiles drawn yet</string><string name="counterFoldOpen">▼</string><string name="counterFoldClosed">▶</string><string name="counterWiremenTechTitle">Technology — remaining bonuses</string><string name="counterWiremenTechBlurb">Total bonus pool from Technology (instant) tiles still in Remaining. Moving a tile to Drawn reduces the bonuses it contributed.</string><string name="wiremenBonusIni0">Initiative 0</string><string name="wiremenBonusIniPlus1">Initiative +1</string><string name="wiremenBonusMatka">Mother</string><string name="wiremenBonusMeleePlus1">Melee attack +1</string><string name="wiremenBonusRangedPlus1">Ranged attack +1</string><string name="deckBack">← Back to Army</string><string name="deckTitle">Set Up Deck</string><string name="deckBlurbStandard">Every deck gets a shareable 6-character code. Anyone using the same code draws tiles in the same order.</string><string name="deckBlurbIronGang">Iron Gang uses a 7-character code: the first 6 set the shuffle order; the 7th sets Hook mode. Mapping: 0 = no Hook, 1 = Mountain, 2 = Boss, 3 = Officer, 4 = Order, 5 = Biker, 6 = Doubled Move, 7 = Fanatic, 8 = Ranged Net Fighter, 9 = Lumberjack. Share the full code so everyone uses the same deck.</string><string name="deckModeNew">🎲 New Random Deck</string><string name="deckModeJoin">🔗 Enter a Code</string><string name="deckYourCode">Your Deck Code</string><string name="deckIronGang7thNote">7th character (highlighted) is random — regenerate for a new Hook mode and shuffle.</string><string name="deckRegenerate">↺ Regenerate</string><string name="deckCopy">⧉ Copy Code</string><string name="deckCopied">✓ Copied!</string><string name="deckShareBlurb">Share this code with other players so everyone draws the same tile order</string><string name="deckShareBlurbIgSuffix"> and Hook option</string><string name="deckEnterCode">Enter Deck Code</string><string name="deckPlaceholderIg">e.g. K7M3PX3</string><string name="deckPlaceholderStd">e.g. K7M3PX</string><string name="deckJoinBlurb">Paste the code shared by another player to draw tiles in the same order</string><string name="deckJoinBlurbIg"> (include all 7 characters).</string><string name="deckStartDrawing">Start Drawing</string><string name="deckErrorCodeLength">Code must be exactly {len} characters.</string><string name="deckErrorInvalid">Invalid code. Please check and try again.</string><string name="deckIgErrorWrongLength">Iron Gang deck code must be exactly 7 characters (6 for shuffle + 1 for Hook mode).</string><string name="deckIgErrorInvalidSeed">Invalid characters in the first 6 positions (shuffle seed).</string><string name="deckIgErrorInvalidSuffix">Invalid 7th character (Hook mode).</string><string name="drawBack">← Army List</string><string name="drawReset">↺ Reset</string><string name="drawMgBanner">Merchants Guild (random mode): Reconnaissance 1 and Reconnaissance 2 are not in the deck at start. After the first Scout Leader is drawn, use Shuffle Reconnaissance 1; after the second Scout Leader, use Shuffle Reconnaissance 2. Each inserts that tile at a random position in the remaining deck (position is deterministic from the deck code).</string><string name="drawIgBannerSuffix">(7th character of the code encodes Hook mode.)</string><string name="drawIgBannerPrefix">Iron Gang (this deck):</string><string name="drawDeckCodeLabelStd">Deck Code — share this to draw in the same order</string><string name="drawDeckCodeLabelIg">Deck Code — first 6 characters = shuffle; 7th = Hook mode</string><string name="drawCopy">⧉ Copy</string><string name="drawCopied">✓ Copied!</string><string name="drawChangeCode">Change Code</string><string name="drawLeft">{n} / {total} left</string><string name="drawProgressDrawn